# Status Updates JSONL

- Append one JSON object per line to [internal/StatusUpdate/status.jsonl](mdc:internal/StatusUpdate/status.jsonl).
- Use the template at [internal/StatusUpdate/STATUS_UPDATE_TEMPLATE.md](mdc:internal/StatusUpdate/STATUS_UPDATE_TEMPLATE.md).
- Validate fields against [internal/StatusUpdate/status.schema.json](mdc:internal/StatusUpdate/status.schema.json) where possible.

Fields
- `ts`: ISO-8601 UTC
- `component`: short area name
- `status`: planned | in_progress | completed | done
- `summary`: 1–3 sentences
- `changes`, `next`: string arrays
- `refs`: `[{type:"file", path:"...", note:"..."}]`
